data.description: You found it... a unique must-see home in a neighborhood that is greatly developed and highly desired. This is a standout with a beautiful open floor plan & gorgeous ceiling detail throughout the home. Wonderful Rock and Brick combination on the exterior. With 3 Bedrooms and 2 baths on a corner lot with a slightly oversized side-entry garage, nice covered patio & wood fenced yard, sprinkler system front & back along with landscaping, this one is the complete package. It also has very nice custom cabinetry & granite throughout along with a great kitchen and a fabulous island open to living & dining. This is definitely not a cookie cutter home! Your home will be the standout in this neighborhood for sure! Come see it today!
